.Dd October 24, 2018
.Dt DLOGDSTAT 8
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm dlogdstat
.Nd Distributed DTrace Log Daemon Monitoring Tool
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Fl p Ar path
.Fl t Ar topic
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
tool monitors the
.Xr dlogd 8
daemon responsible for distributed
.Xr dtrace 1
operation, printing information on one active topic specified using the
.Fl t Ar topic .
.Pp
The arguments must both be specified:
.Bl -tag -width indent
.It Fl p Ar path
Use the
.Nm dlogd
data files found in
.Pa path .
.It Fl t Ar topic
Display information on the topic
.Va topic .
